  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK556">
<l>maṉṉarkku maṉṉutal ceṅkōṉmai yaḵtiṉṟēl </l>
<l>maṉṉāvā maṉṉark koḷi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Righteous government gives permanence to (the fame of) kings without that their fame will have no endurance.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
